snippet.title: Sulfur - Announcement Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/concept/10007890/

🔥 Welcome to SULFUR! 🔥 Dive into the chaotic world of SULFUR, in development for PlayStation! This is our latest trailer showcasing the extensive weapon modification system. Transform your arsenal with a wide range of calibers, attachments, enchantments, and oils, and create the ultimate combat experience. From powerful rifles to niche sidearms, the possibilities are virtually limitless!

#ps5 #ps5games #ps4 #ps4games
